  • P16  Bender 2002    — Tree Layout in Multilevel Memory
  • P17  Bender 2005    — Cache-Oblivious B-Trees
  • P18  Saikkonen 2008 — Multi-Level Block Reorganization
  • P19  Saikkonen 2016 — Layout-Invariant with Constant-Time Updates
  • P21  Chen 2001      — Improving Index Performance through Prefetching
  • P22  Chen 2002      — Fractal Prefetching B+-Trees
  • P23  Khan 2010      — Adaptive Cache Prefetching
  • P24  Naderan-Tahan 2016 — Useless Prefetch study
  • P26  Q. Zhang 2024  — Path/Jump-Pointer Prefetcher (FGCS)
  • P27  T. Zhang 2025  — Hierarchical Bundle Prefetching (ASPLOS;
                          gem5-fork BSD-3 available, not bundled)
